				</section>
				</section>

				<!--=================================slide=====================================-->



					<section id="os3" data-background="#FCDDDD">
					<section>
					
				    <h3><a href="">Monolithic Kernel</a></h3>
				    <div>			
<img src="img/monolithic.png">
<div>
                <div>
                     A monolithic kernel is an operating system architecture where the entire
operating system is working in kernel space and is alone in supervisor mode.
<br>
 It defines a high-level virtual
interface over computer hardware. <br> Set of primitives or system calls
implement all operating system services such as process management,
concurrency, and memory management.	
     </div>
				</section>
				</section>

			

