				    <h3><a href="">why linux is better ....?</a></h3>
				    <h2>Free and Open-source</h2>
				   <ul>
				   	<li>Linux is completely free of charge. </li>
				   	<li>FOSS is computer software that is both free software and open source software. </li>
				   	<li>Anyone is
freely licensed to use, copy, study, and change the software in any way, and
the source code is openly shared. </li>
				   	<li>GNU GPL (General Public License)</li>
				   	<li>Freedom</li>
				   	

				   </ul> 

				    

