				    <h3><a href="">Viruses...? </a></h3>
				    
				   <ul>
				   	<li>Linux is  very well-protected against viruses.</li>
				   	<li>Malware's
lack of root access and fast updates to most Linux vulnerabilities. </li>
				   	<li>Linux :) total known malware = about 60 to 100 </li>
				   	<li>MS Windows :) total known malware = about 60,000 </li>
				   	
				   	

				   </ul> 

				    

				</section>
				</section>


