				     <h3><a href="">Free and unlimited support</a></h3>
				     <p>One of the great assets of the Open Source community (and Linux in
particular), is that it's a real community. Users and developers really are out
there, on web forums, on mailing lists, on IRC channels, helping out new users.
They're all happy to see more and more people switch to Linux, and they're
happy to help them get a grip on their new system.</p>
				   
				 
		

